  "recommendations": [
    "Mamoun Abdelrahim\n\nWorking with Khalid it was always a pleasure. He is the rare individual that combines intelligence, common sense, integrity, passion, sincerity and humor. He would probably prefer to be remembered for his professionalism and his spirit of inclusion for the concerns and interests of all involved in the projects, and he is truly outstanding in these regards, but I remember him best for his sense of humor (He always seemed to have a big smile on his face), his intellectual curiosity and his willingness to see all sides of an issue, even if by doing so he discovered things that made his own path harder. I always admired that about Khalid and I'm sure I'm not the only person who could say so.",
    "Mohamed Al-Harthy\n\nKhalid Khalifa’s leadership performance is expressed through his achievements through the years. His is a visionary business leader and a founder of applied technology companies supporting, influencing and advising various businesses and specially ad-tech business. Khalid has been a pro of high quality in strategy, planning and driving the technology part in mubashir to the performance of excellence. His influence also goes to other related companies including icons...\nI have seen Khalid as a strategic leader as a founding member in strategy meetings and a practical implementer of the agreed plans in execution phase. I have known Khalid since day zero of mubashir…"
  ],
